title: 820-00281 how to test switching mosfet
message:
2016 MacBook Pro 15" A1707 logic board 820-00281-10, how do I test the switching mosfets Q3100, Q3200 etc. I'm suspecting they're the reason battery isn't charging
thanks

title: 820-00281 how to test switching mosfet
message:
Remove them and check out of board.
[URL unfurl="true"]https://www.google.com/search?client=firefox-b-d&q=how+test+mosfet+using+multimeter[/URL]

They should be good, if you get correct PPBUS_G3H without battery.
